	<p class="img-left"><a href="/images/s4p/Wilson_Mendoza_seabird_iceskating.jpg" title="Seabird cruising above the ice" rel="lightbox[s4p]"><img src="/images/s4p/Wilson_Mendoza_seabird_iceskating.jpg" width="130" alt="Seabird cruising above the ice" title="Seabird cruising above the ice"></a><br>
